	(lib_symbols)
	(text_box "HODOR - Highly flexible Open-source Door Operation Regulator\n(A sliding door motor controller)\nHODOR - \"Holds your door\"\n\nA universal controller for brushed DC motors from 12 to 24 V supply voltage\nwith H-bridge driver, current sensor and quadrature encoder or end-switch interface. \nInterfaced by programmable inputs and a relay.\nConfiguration and smart home integration via Wi-Fi."
